{"id": 1480, "genre": 1001, "title": "假期结束，你会给自己设定一套什么样的开工激活程序？", "description": "据说碰到难搞的任务，做点开工小仪式能活过来。（题图来自：Katerina Voronina）", "record_count": 2482, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170203102421Lja1NH9zVpsGmXTr.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-03T03:00:09Z", "options": [{"id": 161280, "content": "红包激活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 576653}, {"id": 161281, "content": "红包激活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 576653}, {"id": 161537, "content": "默默的打开闹铃…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640067}, {"id": 161026, "content": "需要套路么？直接硬启动", "image": null, "praise_count": 370, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690131}, {"id": 161027, "content": "前一天早点睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 198, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922637}, {"id": 162051, "content": "看点向上的名著", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795994}, {"id": 188931, "content": "早起跑步", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926651}, {"id": 161028, "content": "穿新衣服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903903}, {"id": 161540, "content": "玩几天几夜    瘫了 睡了  起来头脑应该会清醒多了 然后会理智的开工", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924728}, {"id": 161029, "content": "滴答清单，个人觉得很好用", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922961}, {"id": 161285, "content": "买东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919847}, {"id": 161286, "content": "来看看而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923753}, {"id": 161798, "content": "准备好抢红包模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925343}, {"id": 161031, "content": "并不打算激活，慢慢就不得不活了", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237112}, {"id": 161287, "content": "3.6才收假", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916846}, {"id": 161543, "content": "进入三月份 每天6点起床 跑步五公里 坚持30天", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913581}, {"id": 161288, "content": "喝点鸡汤，加点砒霜，直接硬重启", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923761}, {"id": 161289, "content": "很认真地玩到很晚，很认真地洗头洗澡，很认真地让头发自然风干，很认真地躺上床盖上被子，很认真地定四个相隔四分钟的闹钟，很认真地给手机充上电……一系列只有做大事前才会做的仪式终于完成了……觉得我活着真累。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847945}, {"id": 161801, "content": "先调整作息时间?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925348}, {"id": 161034, "content": "像慢跑一样，将目标细化成每日任务，然后逐条完成。让自己不要关注太大的问题。每天早点睡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742602}, {"id": 161546, "content": "重装程序", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924742}, {"id": 161035, "content": "喝杯水就是干", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921595}, {"id": 161291, "content": "所在大学为三学期制度，所以，回去就是冬季学期期末考试??‍♂️??‍♂️??‍♂️", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916407}, {"id": 161547, "content": "顺其自然吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 554577}, {"id": 161036, "content": "强行启动", "image": null, "praise_count": 144, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920921}, {"id": 161292, "content": "你是我的过去，过去是忘不掉的过去，还在回忆过去，过去总归是过去??", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906396}, {"id": 161548, "content": "报个网上课程!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924766}, {"id": 161037, "content": "好好在最后一天感受一下家里的软床，因为到了学校就只能睡硬板床！", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923060}, {"id": 161293, "content": "从健身开始，力量型的，跑步也可以，让兴奋激活一切，当然必须有长期运动的基础。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922662}, {"id": 162061, "content": "喝点儿氮泵直接开干 ?‍♂️", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808056}, {"id": 162317, "content": "明天不上班哈哈哈你们恨我吧吖吖一一", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697142}, {"id": 161038, "content": "完全不管手机两小时，静下心来，整理思绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923064}, {"id": 161294, "content": "一年之计在于春", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921381}, {"id": 162830, "content": "静下心来看会儿慢调的书，顺便思考一下人生，知道自己多渺小，就有开工的动力啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892698}, {"id": 161295, "content": "听了一个晚上歌，同一客户确定来访时间，满血复活！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822551}, {"id": 161551, "content": "应该要减肥了吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924772}, {"id": 161296, "content": "制定目标往前冲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890928}, {"id": 161552, "content": "大三狗表示，假期没结束", "image": "img/option/option/20170204205928Iagr5CxYvoFXf9ZV", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260415}, {"id": 161553, "content": "大三狗表示，假期没结束", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260415}, {"id": 162065, "content": "把钱花完  使自己无处可去 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846033}, {"id": 162321, "content": "打扮地帅帅的撩新同事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926182}, {"id": 161042, "content": "赶完假期作业...", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901682}, {"id": 161298, "content": "先健身，让过年新长的肉适应适应", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923801}, {"id": 161043, "content": "换个播音搭档", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525930}, {"id": 161555, "content": "嗯，大扫除和吃东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924774}, {"id": 165139, "content": "我都是顺其自然的，所以感觉现在还没有进状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931888}, {"id": 161044, "content": "重新启动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923072}, {"id": 161300, "content": "从未真正假期", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923812}, {"id": 161045, "content": "过完年，感觉身体被掏空！健身健身健身！！！", "image": "img/option/option/20170203113455BVHhecumIo7U5a4s", "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923073}, {"id": 161301, "content": "吃一顿好的，把自己哄开心，乖宝宝，去上班哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923816}]}